Package: kfigr
Title: Integrated chunk anchoring and referencing for knitr documents.
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2014-06-22
Author: Michael Koohafkan
Maintainer: Michael Koohafkan <michael.koohafkan@gmail.com>
Description: kfigr is a streamlined version of figr designed for tight integration with knitr. The package defines a hook for anchoring code chunks and the ability to track and cross-reference chunks for producing document elements like figures, tables and code blocks.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: knitr (>= 1.6)
Suggests: bibtex, ggplot2
Enhances: kexfig
LazyData: true
VignetteBuilder: knitr
License: GPL-2
